title: [Barefoot Hill, Field]
description: Fallen chunks of crumbling dirt and dried mud have fallen from the huge mound into a pile that nearly conceals the opening of a narrow tunnel leading into the towering structure.

Fallen chunks of crumbling dirt and dried mud have fallen from the huge mound into a pile that nearly conceals the opening of a narrow tunnel leading into the towering structure.  A crumbling stone wall separates the overgrown field from the sparse forest and the road beyond, and an acrid, burnt smell of charred vegetation and something fouler wafts through the cool night air.
